\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14826345 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Yes. Only about 19 - 1923 and '24 or something like that.
