\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16319088 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Did she mend the clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14826345 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16319088 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Where were they bought when you bought clothes?
