ow, you - he was at that time anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16319088 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 You and your brothers and your father went to this tailor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14826345 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Yes. Yes, that's right.
