Well - I think they would be made with - there was quite a lot of - local dressmakers then. Did sewing you know and whatnot, I think they'd - they'd be made at these sewing places you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16319088 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 So you didn't go down to Keighley to the shops, you mainly went to the shops in Haworth?
