\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14826345 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 For work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16319088 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 What about going to school, did you wear them then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14826345 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Yes. For going to school as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16319088 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 So you - only used your shoes for the weekend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14826345 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Yes, that's right, for best, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16319088 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14826345 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16319088 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Did he help with the cleaning at all?
