\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16319088 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Was it a fairly big occasion?
