Why do you think that was, do you think it was because the teacher thought that the others, even if they were prepared for a scholarship, they couldn't take it up because of being poor or was it just that they wanted to help these children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14826345 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 
