\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16319088 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14826345 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 No, not really, apart from the unemployment period, that - that was a bad period really, it kind of changed your outlook on life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16319088 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Did you continue to live at home after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14826345 JS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6582003\charrsid14181391 Yes. Yes.
